data.description: CHARMING home in a small cul-de-sac!  This 3 bedrm/2ba home is very conveniently located near downtown Jackson and near Jackson Jr. High School, the High School and several elementary schools.  Located at the end of the street, it has a relaxing deck off the back that is surrounded by lush landscaping.  Come the Spring you will see a variety of color and smell the wonderful aroma of the blooms.  The master bedroom has its own full bathroom.  If you want to expand downstairs, much of the basement is finished and has a roughed-in bath to make yet another bathroom available.  Plenty of storage space is available there as well.  This home has all newer windows.  Plus, the kitchen has upgrades such as a brand-new state-of-the-art microwave-vent over the stove and a brand-new dishwasher as well.  This is a PROBATE sale and the best contract will go before the court and be approved before the Contract can be officially active.  Be aware of the small time delay in the process.  Come by!
